      "created_at": "2024-10-21T10:45:34.761Z",
      "text": "I just see this as another wave in the old SAIL/MIT war. Currently MIT's connectionist approach is dominant; LLMs are just Minsky's perceptron scaled up to higher-dimensions and focused on semantics.\n\nI talk to folk who are working to add symbolicist approaches back in, which I find intriguing.",
